    "en": {
      "title": "Sotti Upali's younger son was killed in a clash in Borella",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The youngest son of an underworld leader named \"Sothi Upali\" was killed in an incident between two groups in Borella area last night (24th), Borella police said.",
        "A twenty-seven-year-old man named Don Chirantha Gaya Jayasankha or \"Gaia\" of Arambewela, a resident of Borella area, has been stabbed to death.",
        "Police also said that the Additional Magistrate of the Colombo Magistrate Court will conduct the on-site magisterial inquiry into the death today (25)."
      ],
